{"tid":2388785,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國準備正式申請加入跨太平洋貿易區","createTime":"2021-01-31T11:28:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T12:20:48.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f4c22d4026d24f3a1f732ddd504c792e240fd247","tid":2388785,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:28:14.000Z","msg":"英國政府星期天（1月31日）表示，英國將在下周正式申請加入一個有11個成員國的跨太平洋貿易區，並將在今年晚些時候啟動談判。<br />\n<br />\n英國脫離歐盟後，已經明確表示有意加入全面與進步跨太平洋夥伴關係協定（Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership, 簡稱CPTPP）。該協定前身是奧巴馬政府啟動的跨太平洋夥伴關係協定（TPP）。前總統特朗普就任後，宣布美國退出該協定。<br />\n<br />\n目前CPTPP有11個成員國，即澳大利亞、文萊、加拿大、智利、日本、馬來西亞、墨西哥、新西蘭、秘魯、新加坡和越南。個成員國間已經消除了大多數關稅。<br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜在一份聲明中表示：&ldquo;脫離歐盟一年後，我們正在建立新的伙伴關係。這將為英國人民帶來巨大經濟利益。<br />\n<br />\n路透社星期四曾報導，英國將不會遵循此前承諾，在要求加入該協定前發布一個作為CPTPP成員的經濟受益評估報告。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府先前對英國脫歐的分析指出，額外貿易協定對經濟產出推動作用很小。<br />\n<br />\n政府表示，加入CPTPP將取消食品、飲料和汽車關稅，並有助於推動技術和服務業的發展。<br />\n<br />\n聲明表示，英國貿易大臣將在周一與日本和新加坡的貿易官員交談，並正式申請加入CPTPP。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜說：&ldquo;申請成為第一個加入CPTPP的新的國家，表明了我們與世界各地朋友和合作夥伴以最優惠的條件做生意，並成為全球自由貿易的熱情擁護者的雄心。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/506AB5C9-0CB8-40E1-8B2A-06AC999507A8_w408_r1_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2F506AB5C9-0CB8-40E1-8B2A-06AC999507A8_w408_r1_s.jpg&h=46e51fbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跨太平洋11國2018年3月8日簽署《全面與進步跨太平洋夥伴關係協定》（CPTPP）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/uk-brexit-cptpp-/5758477.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fuk-brexit-cptpp-%2F5758477.html&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWgx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=9f1ea1e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/uk-brexit-cptpp-/5758477.html</a>"},{"pid":"626fa92e5c7372ff144c5ac133bdfccd3010b345","tid":2388785,"uid":249162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:31:04.000Z","msg":"支那個亞投行冇撚哂聲氣既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b66b9c71592750ec96c366a94cb4f7a8dbac630","tid":2388785,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:33:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b468a454ee4ff7ebedd5c3e8d7fcae8691c7df","tid":2388785,"uid":301952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"626fa92e5c7372ff144c5ac133bdfccd3010b345","tid":2388785,"uid":249162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:31:04.000Z","msg":"支那個亞投行冇撚哂聲氣既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:35:47.000Z","msg":"外國既野理佢咁多丫<br />\n祝大英祖國成功加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d669dbec4811f3f7655bc831f7cf0b73ff4bc2","tid":2388785,"uid":38982,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:38:18.000Z","msg":"特朗普做唔到總統，到英國接力做佢未做到嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e3f1e62ab60d1bf932d3081e2b820c8277baa1","tid":2388785,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T12:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1bb7b329324f33395af6a72597352ca0e6004b7","tid":2388785,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T12:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba72bef297e8c2513fd3e1df8ca2ac4a22d29bc","tid":2388785,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T12:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}